title: High school football: Benet bounces back from loss, bests Carmel
text:
High school football: Benet bounces back from loss, bests Carmel Published: Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 5:30 a.m. CDT By SUBURBAN LIFE MEDIA 
MUNDELEIN â€“ After a disappointing shutout loss against Nazareth, Benet's football team got back on track with a 28-14 win against Carmel. 
The Redwings improved to 5-2 overall and 3-2 in the East Suburban Catholic Conference, and became eligible for the postseason.
